Gallery::Remote v0.01

Gallery is a web based product that lets you manage your photos on a
web site.

For more information about Gallery visit http://gallery.menalto.com/

Gallery::Remote is a Perl module that provides a Perl Developer
access to the Gallery Remote protocol as described at
http://gallery.menalto.com/modules.php?op=modload&name=GalleryDocs&file=index&page=gallery-remote.protocol.php

Tanner Lovelace
<lovelace-cpan@wayfarer.org>

REQUIREMENTS
  - LWP::UserAgent        - Handles communication with the Gallery server.
  - HTTP::Cookies         - Gallery remote authentication requires cookies.
  - HTTP::Request::Common - Used for POST requests.

INSTALLATION

  perl Makefile.PL
  make
  make install

STATUS

Initial release.  I'm sure it's riddled wtih bugs.  Please report
them to lovelace-cpan@wayfarer.org.

2004/02/17

